"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-australia-news-politics-albanese-government-announces-almost-half-a-billion-in-funding-for-elite-athletes-ahead-of-2024-paris-olympics-news-story-6d3e254c61c197a4875f3ac0363180f9\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Albanese government has announced almost $500 million in funding over two years for elite athletes ahead of the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prime Minister Anthony Albanese has announced almost half a billion dollars in funding for elite athletes in the lead-up to the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking at the Australian Institute of Sport on Friday, Mr Albanese detailed the government's investment strategy as it targets future success at the 2032 Brisbane Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Albanese government has provided an additional $283 million on top of existing funding for elite sports.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This $283 million in new money, on top of the annual funding that we give, will make a significant difference over the next two years,\\\" Mr Albanese said.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prime Minister emphasised this represents a 50 per cent increase on the Morrison government's 2021-22 high performance funding for the Tokyo Olympic Games and a \\\"doubling\\\" of paralympic athlete funding.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morrison_government\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Morrison government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morrison_government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morrison_government\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Including the $102 million in annual grant funding, the announcement will bring the Albanese government's total high-performance investment to $489 million over two years.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Prime Minister said he hoped the funding would \\\"assist in Paris\\\" for the Summer Olympic Games from July 26 to August 11 - and also prepare younger athletes for Brisbane 2032.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999988188044582, \"rank\": 1.1811969697572523e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The bottom line is I want to set up our youngest Australians for success at our own Olympic Games in Brisbane in 2032,\\\" Mr Albanese said.\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1408, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999269692534744, \"rank\": 5.7462489021661205e-05, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}, {\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are a sporting nation and when our athletes are doing well, it lifts up our entire nation and inspires us.\\\"\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as providing a competitive edge, the Prime Minister promoted the benefits of participation in sport including improved mental wellbeing, lifestyle and social skills.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Albanese said he hoped the investment would help get children off their phones and into the pool or onto the sporting field.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"President of the Australian Olympic Committee Ian Chesterman welcomed the investment as \\\"very good news\\\" that would help athletes represent Australia on the international stage.\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1880, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1909, \"end\": 1923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Chesterman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ian Chesterman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Chesterman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ian_Chesterman\"}, {\"begin\": 2003, \"end\": 2012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"score\": 0.9838995152094284, \"rank\": 0.016344035890505374, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This funding increase is a very important start to help our athletes be their best, inspire the generations to come and to build a strong sports system,\\\" Mr Chesterman said.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"President of Paralympics Australia Alison Creagh also praised the investment and declared it would \\\"bring about monumental generational change for Para-sport\\\".\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2231, \"end\": 2252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympics_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympics Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympics_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympics_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2253, \"end\": 2259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"score\": 0.999999994641712, \"rank\": 4.701974788830209e-09, \"text\": \"Alison\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alison_DiLaurentis\"}, {\"begin\": 2260, \"end\": 2266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skibbereen\", \"score\": 0.999999755581969, \"rank\": 2.4375626130080575e-07, \"text\": \"Creagh\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skibbereen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skibbereen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": []}]}"